title: CLEAR_ENTITY_LAST_DAMAGE_ENTITY
content:
0xA72CD9CA74A5ECBA0x2B83F43B// ClearEntityLastDamageEntity
void CLEAR_ENTITY_LAST_DAMAGE_ENTITY(Entity entity);Parameters:entity: The entity to clear the last damaging entity from.This native could affect the arguments of the CEventNetworkEntityDamage game event, by clearing the damaging entity before the event is fired.
codeBlocks:
local entity = PlayerPedId()
-- Example usage for CLEAR_ENTITY_LAST_DAMAGE_ENTITY
ClearEntityLastDamageEntity(entity)
